author: eTN Editor
title: Kuwait Airways launches Munich to Kuwait City flights
text:
Kuwait Airways launches Munich to Kuwait City flights Adv: 
Jul 17, 2015 Adv: 
Kuwait Airwaysâ€™ inaugural flight from Munich, Germany, to Kuwait City was celebrated with a traditional ribbon-cutting ceremony. The new route will be served with A340 jetliners. 
Among those in attendance (pictured) were (from left): Andreas von Puttkamer (Head of Aviation, Munich Airport), Dr. Michael Kerkloh (President and CEO, Munich Airport), Philip Saunders (CCO, Kuwait Airways) and Mohammed Al-Enezi (Manager of German Operations, Kuwait Airways).
